{"thag1.1:0.1":"Theragatha 1.1 ","thag1.1:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag1.1:0.4":"Subhutittheragatha ","thag1.1:1.0.1":"Nidanagatha ","thag1.1:1.0.2":"Namo tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sammasambuddhassa. ","thag1.1:1.1":"Sihanamva nadantanam, ","thag1.1:1.2":"dathinam girigabbhare; ","thag1.1:1.3":"Sunatha bhavitattanam, ","thag1.1:1.4":"gatha atthupanayika. ","thag1.1:2.1":"Yathanama yathagotta, ","thag1.1:2.2":"yathadhammaviharino; ","thag1.1:2.3":"Yathadhimutta sappanna, ","thag1.1:2.4":"viharimsu atandita. ","thag1.1:3.1":"Tattha tattha vipassitva, ","thag1.1:3.2":"phusitva accutam padam; ","thag1.1:3.3":"Katantam paccavekkhanta, ","thag1.1:3.4":"imamatthamabhasisum. ","thag1.1:4.0":"Subhutittheragatha ","thag1.1:4.1":"“Channa me kutika sukha nivata, ","thag1.1:4.2":"Vassa deva yathasukham; ","thag1.1:4.3":"Cittam me susamahitam vimuttam, ","thag1.1:4.4":"Atapi viharami vassa deva”ti. ","thag1.1:4.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma subhutitthero gatham abhasitthati. "}